  • Tableau : social

  slice(1:6) %>%

social %>% 
  slice(9:10) %>%
  rename("Sexe" = age) %>%

  slice(22:24) %>%

  pivot_longer(cols = !Enfant & !total_workers &!other_percent,

  rename("Salaire" = age) %>%
  pivot_longer(cols = !Salaire & !total_workers &!other_percent, 
               names_to = "Methode", values_to = "Percent") -> Salaire
